{"tid":645182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長髮熱褲女獨行旺角被搶環保袋　西九EU迅速拉人起贓","createTime":"2018-04-28T01:51:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T02:42:09.000Z","uid":107611,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bccb08e4e893b9f48a912b381f1ae518ca3f6fb5","tid":645182,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:51:23.000Z","msg":"今日（28日）凌晨近5時，一名身穿超短牛仔褲的20多歲長髮少女，獨自行經旺角花園街與太子道西交界時，突被一名30餘歲男子，從後搶去其黑色環保袋，賊人得手後拔足狂奔逃去，女事主登時被嚇至花容失色，高聲呼救及報警。西九龍衝鋒隊接報後迅速趕抵現場，並在附近一帶兜截，成功截獲疑犯拘捕，贓物亦於附近花園街的排檔尋回，案件列作搶劫處理，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1399695/org/d5050c6b27d8a70fa5f1eaba26ebe6da.jpg/k6zQwjPQSXhNnE0-yKjYLV5V92IxJb_d9BxklfQcZJU?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1399695%2Forg%2Fd5050c6b27d8a70fa5f1eaba26ebe6da.jpg%2Fk6zQwjPQSXhNnE0-yKjYLV5V92IxJb_d9BxklfQcZJU%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=159ea7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1399697/org/7b60805e6d78ebc0fce4d7b21d470806.jpg/has_rbILmCqQ_VipmVODZkwmHNqumXB4ttEk27bRJNs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1399697%2Forg%2F7b60805e6d78ebc0fce4d7b21d470806.jpg%2Fhas_rbILmCqQ_VipmVODZkwmHNqumXB4ttEk27bRJNs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=abd58c64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b53f9d640f1f6ccb37846342578ba2bb9eb1c35","tid":645182,"uid":135949,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"攞番個袋都要衝鋒隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb3ddb21d3c2ff22c7af88bb27c8d150143d07e","tid":645182,"uid":107611,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3b53f9d640f1f6ccb37846342578ba2bb9eb1c35","tid":645182,"uid":135949,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"攞番個袋都要衝鋒隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-2